{
  "chapter": 77,
  "chapter_summary": "第七十七回 高明的手段\n\n孙老先生与孙小红在决斗场地分析李寻欢与上官金虹决斗前的心理博弈。孙老先生详细讲解李寻欢探测战场的深层用意：选择最佳站位避开夕阳刺眼、探测枯枝坚牢程度以防上官金虹做手脚、为可能的树梢战斗做准备。孙老先生指出，真正的高手决斗在正式出手前就已开始，胜负取决于细心、耐力与智慧。\n\n孙小红为李寻欢的安危忧心忡忡，跪求祖父出手相救。孙老先生答应保护李寻欢，祖孙二人温情互动。然而孙老先生眼中的深沉悲哀暗示他已预见某种不可逆转的命运。\n\n夜晚，李寻欢在八角亭顶发现上官金虹留下的铁匣子，内装一束黑色长发。上官金虹意图借此动摇李寻欢心智，让他怀疑这头发属于林诗音。孙老先生指出这是高明的心理战术——既不留要挟把柄，又足以扰乱对手心神。李寻欢明知是计却无法不在意，陷入两难困境，感叹命运弄人。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "后天他来的时候，上官金虹必定已先到了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "怎见得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为先来的人，就有权先占据最佳地势，上官金虹当然不肯错过这机会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "那么，李寻欢为什么不跟他争先？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许他从不愿和别人争先，也许……他还有别的用意。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小李探花并不是个普通人，他的用意，有时连我都猜不透。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "以我看来，这里所有的地方都差不多……我实在看不出最佳地势在哪里。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在现在他站着的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "他站的这地方和别的地方又有什么不同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上官金虹站在这里，李寻欢势要在他对面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "决斗的时候，正是太阳下山的时候……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我明白了，夕阳往这边照过去，站在那边的人，难免被阳光刺着眼珠，只要他眼睛一刻那看不见，就给了对方杀他的机会。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "上官金虹既然一定会站在这地方，他站在这里干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他站在这里，才能发现这地方有什么弱点，才能决定自己要站在什么地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看，夕阳照在枯林上，也有闪光，因为枯枝上已有秋霜，所以站在这里的人，眼睛也有被闪光刺着的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你明白了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上只知小李飞刀，例不虚发，却不知他轻功之高，也很少有人能比得上。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "但他这又是在干什么呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是在试探那边的枯枝是否坚牢，容不容易折断，这又有两种作用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "哪两种？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "第一，他怕上官金虹在枯枝上做手脚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "什么样的手脚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当他面对着上官金虹时，树上的枯枝若是突然断了，就会怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "枯枝断了，自然就会掉下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "掉在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "当然是掉在地上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "也许就掉在他面前，也许就掉在他头上，他就难免会分心，一分心上官金虹就又有了杀他的机会。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有，到了万不得已时，他只有往树上退，以轻功来扳回劣势，那时树梢就成了他们的战场。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "所以他必须将每一棵树的情况都先探测一遍，就正如他探测这里的土质一样。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你现在总算明白了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论做什么，做到高深时，就是种学问，就连做衣服、炒菜，也是一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们的决斗之期虽然在后天，其实远在他们第一次见面时就已开始，这段时候才是真正考验他们细心、耐力、智慧的时候，他们的胜负，在这段时候里就已决定，到了真正出手时，一刻那间就可解决了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但别人却只能看到那一瞬间的事，所以人们常说‘武林高手一招争’，又谁知道他们为了那一招曾经花了多少功夫？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个真正的高手活在世上，必定是寂寞的，因为别人只能看到他们辉煌的一面，看不到他们所牺牲的代价，所以根本就没有人能了解他。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但他们是不是需要别人了解呢？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别人都以为李寻欢疏忽大意的人，又有谁能看到他小心仔细的一面？到了真正重要的关头，他真是一点地方都不肯放过。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这也许是因为他放过的已太多了……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这一战既然早已开始，以你老人家看，到现在为止他们是谁占了优势？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁也没有占到优势。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看……上官金虹对自己好像比较有信心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，这只因近年来他无论做什么事都是无往不利，一帆风顺，可是，他儿子的死对他却是个很大的打击。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有荆无命，荆无命一走，他的损失也很大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以他急着要找李寻欢决斗，为的就是怕自己的信心消失。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以这一战不仅关系他两人的生死胜负，也关系着整个武林的命运。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "关系这么大？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为这一战上官金虹若是胜了，他对自己的信心必定更强，做事必定更没有顾忌，到了那时，世上只怕也真没有人能制得住他了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我忽然觉得这一战他是必定胜不了的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小李飞刀，例不虚发，他的飞刀从未失手过！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上官金虹也从未败过！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你老人家莫忘了，他曾经败过一次的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那天，在洛阳城外的长亭里，他岞非就曾经败在你老人家手下？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "局时有雾。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我只求你老人家千万莫要让李寻欢死，千万不能……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这世上只有你老人家一个能制得住上官金虹，只有你老人家一个人能救他，你老人家总该知道，他若死了，我也没法子活下去的。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是我孙女中最调瘾的一个，你若死了，以后还有谁会来拔我的胡子，掐我的头发？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你答应了？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说来说去，为的就是要等我说这句话？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你老人家总该知道，女大不中留，女儿的心，总是向外的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你的脸皮若还是这么厚，人家敢不敢要你，我可不知道。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道，他不要我也有法子要他要。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是我最喜欢的孙女，但却太调瘾，胆子也太大，一直担心你找不到婚家，现在你总算找到了一个你自己喜欢的，我乜替你欢喜。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我找到他，算我运气，他找到我，也算是他的运气，像我这样的人，这天下也许还没有几个。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了你之外，简直连一个都没有。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你在上面干什么？为什么还不下来？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是谁的头发？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么长的头发，一定是女人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论如何，这只不过是几根头发而已，有什么好奇怪的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "有什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪，而且很奇怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "哪点奇怪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很多点怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "头发怎会在铁匡子里？铁匡子怎会在亭子顶上？是谁将它放上去的？有什么用意？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是我猜得不错，这必定是上官金虹的近作。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上官金虹？他这样做是为了什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就为了要让李寻欢看到这束头发。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是……可是他……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他算准了李寻欢一定会先来探测战场，也算准了他一定会到亭子上去，所以就先将这匢子留在那里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是这头发又有什么特别呢？就算看到了也不会怎么样呀，他这么样做岂非很滑稻？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你知道这是谁的头发？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你能不能确定？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你也不能确定，是不是？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上官金虹这么样做，就要你认为这头发是林诗音的，要你认为她已落入他的掌握，要你的心不定，他才好杀你，你为何要上他的当？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，林姐妰若真的已落入他手里，他为什么不索性当面来要挟你？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他不能这么样做——别人能，他却不能。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他为什么不能？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若有人知道上官金虹是用这种手段才胜了李寻欢的，岞非要被天下人耻笑？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但现在他什么也没有说，只不过让你看到了一束头发而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这正是他的手段高明之处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这头发也许并不是她的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许不是，也许是……谁也不能确定。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你若完全不去理会，就当做根本没有看到，他的心计岂非就白费了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜我已经看到了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就因为他什么也没有说，所以你才怀疑，就因为他算准了你会怀疑，所以才这么样做，你也明知道他的用意，却偏偏还要落入他的圈套。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种荒唐的事，为什么偏偏要让我遇到？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 77,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 419
    }
  ],
